              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33927686/" class="">“我们必须全力以赴，同时又不抱任何希望。”</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/echocf1120/" class=" " title="—ECHO—">—ECHO—</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
